------------------------------------------------------------------------------
HELP CALL
------------------------------------------------------------------------------

CALL SYSOP

    Using this, You may call the sysop to have a chat. The call may be aborted
    by pressing Cntrl-X.

    ACCESS: CLASS 00


CALL PAUSE

    This command stops the system and disables the line timeout. However, the
    session timeout is not affected. To continue enter Cntrl-X.

    ACCESS: CLASS 01

